<br>
Look, you seem to be asking for some advise, so here is some honest advise.  The problem isn't that you are trying to rival anyone at anything, the problem is just that you are trying so damn hard.  This isn't a competition.  I know that might seem difficult to understand sometimes, because people sometimes treat it that way, but there is a subtle distinction.  When I am &quot;competing&quot; with my friend to see who can show off the best scar, no one really cares who wins.  It's just fun.  Most of the &quot;competing&quot; you see around here is of that sort.  A lot of the rest is just nasty, and then the odd time there might be some genuine rivalry.  But that's it.<br>
<br>
Believe it or not, going around and trying to win at everything is not an effective life strategy.  I've been watching your posts for ages.  &quot;I'm the youngest planes raider.&quot;  &quot;I can roleplay gooder than you.&quot;  &quot;See?  I'm cool also....&quot;  I'm sorry bud, but you are constantly hanging yourself out to dry by demanding approval where no approval is necessary.  And then you wonder why people end up shooting you down.  You almost force them to, by demanding they either play up to your own image of yourself or say something to deflate it.  Your age wouldn't be such a damn issue if you weren't constantly drawing attention to it as some kind of benchmark, like you have somehow gotten the scoop on all the rest of us by being younger than we are.  Seriously, we wouldn't care if you just didn't care.  When was the last time you saw someone bragging about being the oldest player of EQ?<br>
<br>
So, yeah.  Just calm down.  Work hard at impressing the kids your age, it might work better.  Probably not, never worked for me, but you never know.  Maybe you are just more impressive than I was.  But as you wander into high school, you might find those unwritten social rules are more like what you find here rather than what you got in middle school.<br>
<br>
In your own way you are a pretty cool kid Magiith.  The only damn thing about you is you seem to need to hear that every five fucking minutes.  So remember I said it this time.  Print it and put it on your wall if you need to.  Cause this is the one time you get it from me.<br>
<br>
Good luck.<br>
<br>
