I have a very big beef with SOE's policy towards allowing children to play the game and if I had the money, I would probably litigate to have your right to play the game removed, Magiith. Its not personal, I just don't other peoples' kids in my free time. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Nakath Thunderbush<br>
