Honestly, lets not go overboard. While I believe parents should be involved in their child's life, and occasionally walking over to surprise them and check up on what they're doing and read over a little bit what they're saying -- I do not believe it requires constant supervision, nor do I believe that people below the age of 18 should loose their right to play this game.<br>
